This paper deals with analyzing images using deep learning techniques, which is a common topic in the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper focuses on predicting daily activities, which falls under the human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Finally, the paper also incorporates contextual information, such as time and day of week, which could be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR).
